They are CSS preprocessors that extend the functionality of traditional CSS, allowing the use of variables, nesting, mixins, and other features to write styles more efficiently and modularly.

It is a CSS framework that provides a set of predefined classes to style components and create layouts quickly and consistently. It is based on the 'utility-first' philosophy, which means it focuses on providing utility classes for specific styles rather than predefined components.

SQL, or Structured Query Language, is a programming language used to interact with relational databases. It allows for querying, inserting, updating, and deleting data, as well as defining and modifying the structure of databases. It is widely used in web and software development to efficiently and securely manage and manipulate data
